{
  "stem": "10283.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But my eyes were very bad, and they wouldn't take me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I even had traveled to Berlin by myself to be re-examined, to have my eyes re-examined.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And on the morning that we-- we were already on the train, and my grandfather was at the train, and he brought me the letter that I was finally accepted.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I-- it was too late, and maybe it was for the best.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a lot of my girlfriends, and especially from that youth organization, went on Youth Aliyah to-- to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And still-- some are still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you-- were both sets of grandparents alive at this time when you were leaving?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, my grandmother, my father's mother, was a window, yeah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the other set was still--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, they were both-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know how we-- because we were very close with the grandparents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but my mother had always had a vision that she will send for them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while we're there, while we're in Cuba, we will get visas for them too, and they will follow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a rationalization, but, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they had me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a young daughter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they probably felt that it was more important for the young people to-- to leave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I-- today, I never understood quite how they could leave them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But today as I got older, I, you know, I understand it a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, we got on the-- on the Saint Louis, and we-- going there was fine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was a German ship, but it was not like on the Nazi.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
